WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
[Synthesizer initializing. Push 2 pads illuminate in a grid layout.]

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
[Pad pressed. C major chord. "Cmaj" displayed on Push screen.]

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
[Synthesized piano-like chord tone plays. Pads for C, E, and G light up.]

00:12.000 --> 00:16.000
[Pad pressed. A minor chord. "Am" displayed on Push screen.]

00:16.000 --> 00:20.000
[Chord tone changes. Pads for A, C, and E light up.]

00:20.000 --> 00:24.000
[Pad pressed. F major chord. "Fmaj" displayed on Push screen.]

00:24.000 --> 00:28.000
[Synthesized chord tone plays. Pads for F, A, and C light up.]

00:28.000 --> 00:32.000
[Pad pressed. G major chord. "Gmaj" displayed on Push screen. Audio fades out.]
